{"tid":1823034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人睇完被跳樓既片有咩感受?","createTime":"2020-01-13T10:54:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T12:58:43.000Z","uid":307908,"like":17,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c428bb38d47eac0899f8731ddcfa7fcf7c43960b","tid":1823034,"uid":307908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T10:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：習慣了 (情緒一早被港共玩爆了)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：依然憤怒、傷感<br />\n<br />\n老實講：一直以黎都係被自殺，點解而家要等到有片被跳樓先憤怒。我可能開始無左情緒，只係想諗香港日後仲有無出路，點先有第二個轉折點。"},{"pid":"648506e9dcecbb6fae99e490fee1c235d740cd11","tid":1823034,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcf37c675326f719a79755669a5c3ce2eb05ad75","tid":1823034,"uid":266755,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"喪盡天良"},{"pid":"9105ab0295f90f6047e5f03374cde2e8d2e722b5","tid":1823034,"uid":160916,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"請真<br />\n一開始睇完我係冇感覺<br />\n<br />\n但係當我發現自己咁嘅時候<br />\n就知道我已經中咗政府同黑警一直以嚟嘅奸計<br />\n佢哋不停做衰嘢<br />\n到真係有大獲嘢發生都會令人冇咩感覺<br />\n<br />\n同自己講唔可以咁落去<br />\n之後就開咗個whatsapp 周圍share同埋討論<br />\n拎令團火出嚟"},{"pid":"41d4e1ab1c7befc2631afbe300d0c644e88120ec","tid":1823034,"uid":84982,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:11:10.000Z","msg":"唔好下下跳樓都屈人<br />\n就係成日鳩屈先搞到人無感<br />\n公信力都無埋"},{"pid":"f738f97dda53fb4ca9064337c56dd473abe2b8fe","tid":1823034,"uid":217228,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"今晚食咩好?"},{"pid":"4ec206c9cc643964c3891b1142f04b9b0bc08d43","tid":1823034,"uid":50894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T11:13:55.000Z","msg":"好撚迷失..."},{"pid":"c5b579d5e8aaec963e1dc89d68e09024cf53515c","tid":182